Package nswalke4.smallbpayroll.util

Class PayPeriod

  • java.lang.Object
    • nswalke4.smallbpayroll.util.PayPeriod
  • public class PayPeriod
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a representation of the PayPeriod table from the database used for the payroll application, as well as the two enumerators used by the account object in the database.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      static class  PayPeriod.PayPeriodType
      This enumerator represents all of the different possible pay-period types that can be used with this payroll application.
